snippet.title: Gotham Knights - Official Nightwing Character Trailer
snippet.description:
Gotham City’s Knight in blue is on a mission. 

From Flying Grayson, to Robin, to his own hero, Nightwing continues the fight for the city that gave him everything. Gotham City is his home and the people, his family. He’s got this. 

Pre-order Gotham Knights and get the 233 Kustom Batcycle Skin. 

#Nightwing #GothamKnights

Learn more: http://go.wbgames.com/GothamKnights
